      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Hebrews 7:14",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ",) which was a far greater privilege than the birthright. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "But, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "or ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "although, the birthright was Joseph’s — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "So this prevents or removes an objection to Judah’s precedency taken from the birthright.",
        "children": []
